---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Shutdown Assistant. How we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="px-4 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl prose prose-slate">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email address (when purchasing guides or requesting agent service)</li>
        <li>Payment information (processed by Stripe; we do not store card numbers)</li>
        <li>Business information (when using the shutdown agent service)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We automatically collect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Usage data (pages visited, features used)</li>
        <li>Device and browser information</li>
        <li>IP address</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Deliver purchased guides and services</li>
        <li>Process payments</li>
        <li>Communicate about your order or service</li>
        <li>Improve the Service</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share information only with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Stripe (payment processing)</li>
        <li>Government agencies (only when filing on your behalf with the shutdown agent service, and only with your authorization)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information by contacting privacy@shutdownassistant.com.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy: privacy@shutdownassistant.com</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
